text: The Arnhem Coast, an interim Australian bioregion, is located in the Northern Territory,IBRA Version 6.1 data comprising an area of of the coastal plains that characterises central Arnhem Land in the Top End of the Northern Territory. ==See also== * Geography of Australia ==References== Category:Arnhem Land Category:Arnhem Land tropical savanna Category:Biogeography of the Northern Territory Category:Coastline of the Northern Territory Category:IBRA regions
